{"tid":1823732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「突發」中國專欄作家屈穎妍借澳州天災羞辱澳洲！","createTime":"2020-01-14T02:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T05:30:40.000Z","uid":149494,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eab0f09cf5fd5934831bab9317f94d6bd7aa2e3c","tid":1823732,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍：<br />\n<br />\n最近在微博看到一位東北青年的文章，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寫的是澳洲山火，慶幸的是生而為中國人</span></span>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  「以前，我總覺得國外的月亮就是圓。看過幾本書，關注過幾個公知後，我認定：西方人民的生活，才是民主的全部。我和所有憤青一樣，在網上罵國家、罵政府，覺得生活裏所有不如意，都是中國欠自己的。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直到看到澳洲政府處理山火的新聞後，我才有多慶幸，自己沒生在這樣的國家。</span></span>」"},{"pid":"db0c752e5be95434baf050617342e68f860a25aa","tid":1823732,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"290a0b84d22387e12a73e3b48a30d510161792c5","tid":1823732,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xy8dnJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXy8dnJ6.jpg&h=499555ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzHtV36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyzHtV36.jpg&h=09ac52e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ff40ac672c6cc0347dbd18cb35ea981f19966f7","tid":1823732,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:47:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"077a3efca19963fbeb344069360f732f9ee50959","tid":1823732,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"本身就係地理問題<br />\n唔同區都有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國唔洗山火已經乜都睇唔到"},{"pid":"4a8a0548c04caf0486cf7fc0e79880d692f33626","tid":1823732,"uid":121197,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-